text: I'm Thinking of Ending Things (written as i'm thinking of ending things in lowercase) is a 2020 American psychological horror movie written and directed by Charlie Kaufman. It stars Jesse Plemons, Jessie Buckley, Toni Collette, and David Thewlis. It is based on the 2016 novel of the same name by Iain Reid. It was released on Netflix on September 4, 2020. ==Cast== ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:American psychological movies Category:American horror movies Category:Movies set in Oklahoma Category:Movies based on books Category:2020 horror movies Category:Netflix movies
